## EXAMPLE FINDING

```yaml
finding:
  id: WF-001
  category: Workflow
  subcategory: Data Entry
  severity: MEDIUM
  file: src/pages/forms/DailyEquipmentInspectionForm.tsx
  line: 120-145
  observed_condition: |
    User must manually enter truck_number, chipper_number, 
    trailer_number each day even though they use same equipment.
  evidence: |
    // No smart defaults, no recent values, no user preferences
    const [truckNumber, setTruckNumber] = useState('');
    const [chipperNumber, setChipperNumber] = useState('');
  impact: |
    Employees waste 30-60 seconds per form entering same 
    equipment numbers. With 50 employees × 5 days = 250 
    submissions/week = 2-4 hours wasted weekly.
  recommendation: |
    Use existing useSmartDefaults hook to pre-fill equipment 
    numbers from user's most recent submission.
  dod: |
    1. Open equipment inspection form
    2. Equipment numbers auto-populate from last submission
    3. User can override if needed
    4. Time to complete form reduced by 30+ seconds
  effort: S
  dependencies: none
```

